 Trailer Dr. Tests"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"capabilities-list","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Brake, turn, running, and marker lights"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Electrical connections and wiring faults"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"ABS fault code reading via industry-standard blink codes. Works on all major trailer brands. No software, no subscriptions, no proprietary dongles required."}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Air supply to the trailer (125 lb max, self-regulated)"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Air leaks"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Brake activation and air brake response"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"One-person operation via manual controls or wireless remote"}]]}]]}]]}]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"section section--muted","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"section-label","children":"Built for the Field"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"section-title","children":"Smallest Unit. Most Power. No Compromises."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"section-subtitle","children":"Competing trailer testers sacrifice size for power or require vehicle mounting. Trailer Dr. does neither."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"features-field-grid","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"features-field-card","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"material-symbols-outlined features-field-card__icon","aria-hidden":"true","children":"scale"}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"Compact and Easy to Carry"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"15.2 lbs at 12 x 10 x 4 in. The smallest in its class. Works with any 115V outlet and air supply."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"features-field-card","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"material-symbols-outlined features-field-card__icon","aria-hidden":"true","children":"bolt"}],["$","h3",null,{"children":"Most Powerful in Its Class"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"30A @ 12.8 VDC. 2/3rds more power than leading competitors."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"feature